OL,3,CMan from Eastbourne charged with
OL,4,Cterrorism offences
OL,6,FA 35-year-old man is set to appear in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with encouraging
OL,8,Fterrorism.
OL,10,FMohammed Abdulkalik Fadil Alazawi, of
OL,11,FBedford Grove in Eastbourne, East
OL,12,FSussex, is accused of three counts of
OL,13,Fencouraging people to commit, prepare
OL,14,For instigate acts of terrorism.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
