PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773072686
OL,3,CMan from Eastbourne charged with
OL,4,Cterrorism offences
OL,6,FIt comes after counter-terror officers
OL,7,Farrested a man on Friday on suspicion
OL,8,Fof expressing an opinion in support of
OL,9,Fthe so-called Islamic State group -
OL,10,Falso know as Daesh - as part of an
OL,11,Finvestigation into Islamist terrorism
OL,12,Frelated to posts on social media
OL,13,Fplatforms.
OL,15,FThe operation was led by Counter
OL,16,FTerrorism Policing South East with
OL,17,Fsupport from Sussex Police.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
