PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773072686
OL,3,CMan from Eastbourne charged with
OL,4,Cterrorism offences
OL,6,FOn Friday, Sussex Police Chief
OL,7,FSuperintendent Justin Burtensaw said:
OL,8,F"I appreciate arrests of this nature
OL,9,Fcan cause people in the local
OL,10,Fcommunity tofeel unsettled, however
OL,11,FSussex Police has been working closely
OL,12,Fto support our colleagues in Counter
OL,13,FTerrorism Policing South East as part
OL,14,Fof this pre-planned operation.
OL,16,F"There is not believed to be any
OL,17,Fimmediate risk to those in the
OL,18,Fcommunity but I would urge anyone who
OL,19,Fhas any concerns to contact police."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
