OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773072686
OL,3,CMan from Eastbourne charged with
OL,4,Cterrorism offences
OL,6,FAlazawi was charged on Saturday and
OL,7,Fhas been remanded into custody.
OL,9,FHe will appear at Westminster
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court on Monday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
